    <title> Goat Cheese/ Beetroot Salad </title>
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <h1> Goat Cheese/ Beetroot Salad </h1>
    <p> <img src= "goatcheesebeetrootsalad.jpg" alt= "" width= "450" height= "300"> </p>
	
    <h2> Ingredients </h2>
    <ul>
      <li> Lettuce/ Any leafy salad base you like. </li>
      <li> Beetroot (cut into slices). </li>
      <li> Goats Cheese (cut into slices). </li>
      <li> Walnuts (crush up a bit). </li>
      <li> Balsamic Dressing (you can also make your own if you know how lol). </li>
    </ul>
	
    <h2> Method </h2>
    <ol>  
      <li> Put lettuce/ leafy salad on plate. </li>
      <li> Add beetroot and goats cheese on the top. </li>
      <li> Sprinkle crushed walnuts on top. </li>
      <li> Drizzle balsamic dressing over. </li>
   </ol>
	  </body>

